NETHERLANDS COASTGUARD
NAVIGATIONAL WARNING - ADDITIONAL NR. 66 130506 UTC MAR
WAVE HEIGHT WARNING 300CM TSS TERSCHELLING - GERMAN BIGHT
ISSUED AT 130500 UTC MAR
CONTAINER VESSELS WITH A LENGTH OF 100-200M
ARE AT RISK OF LOSING CONTAINERS DURING HEAVY SEA CONDITIONS
IN PARTICULAR FROM A WEST-NORTHWEST TO NORTHERLY DIRECTION.
THESE VESSELS SHOULD ALTER COURSE IF NECESSARY TO AVOID
COMING ABEAM TO THE WAVES AND TAKE OTHER APPROPRIATE
MEASURES TO AVOID LOSING CONTAINERS.
